Absolutely! I'll create a completely ad-free version of the educational gaming portal. Since the original version I made didn't actually have any ads anyway, this will be a cleaner, more focused version with enhanced educational features.

# **EduPortal Pure - Ad-Free Educational Gaming Platform**

